    "fact_id": "D1.12-risk-treatment",
    "scope": "D1",
    "claim_type": "concept",
    "status": "active",
    "claim": "The four risk treatment options are: Accept (tolerate the risk), Avoid (eliminate the risk-creating activity), Transfer/Share (e.g., insurance), and Mitigate/Reduce (apply controls to lower likelihood or impact). The mnemonic is AATR.",
    "source": "cc-master-learning-center/reference/cc-exam-blueprint.md#risk-management-fundamentals",
